title: Criticism of Psychiatry and  Psychoanalysis - Collection 6
description:
Criticism of Psychiatry and  Psychoanalysis - Collection 6:

We have 24 titles here:

-  Bell (Ed.) - Psychoanalysis and Culture; a Kleinian Perspective (2004)

-  Boag - Freudian Repression, the Unconscious, and the Dynamics of Inhibition (2012)

-  Bolle (Ed.) - Deleuze and Psychoanalysis; Philosophical Essays on Deleuze's Debate with Psychoanalysis (2010)

-  Cooper - The Quiet Revolution in American Psychoanalysis; Selected Papers of Arnold M. Cooper (2005)

-  Cordon - Freud's World; an Encyclopedia of His Life and Times (2012)

-  Corsini & Wedding - Current Psychotherapies, 8e (2008)

-  Diamond & Christian (Eds.) - The Second Century of Psychoanalysis; Evolving Perspectives on Therapeutic Action (2011)

-  Fromm - Beyond the Chains of Illusion; My Encounter with Marx and Freud (1962)

-  Helmchen & Sartorius (Eds.) - Ethics in Psychiatry; European Contributions (2010)

-  Jung - Jung Contra Freud; the 1912 New York Lectures on the Theory of Psychoanalysis (1961)

-  Kline - Fact and Fantasy in Freudian Theory, 2e (1981)

-  Langs - Freud on a Precipice; How Freud's Fate Pushed Psychoanalysis over the Edge (2010)

-  Lehmann (Ed.) - Coming off Psychiatric Drugs; Successful Withdrawal from Neuroleptics, Antidepressants, Mood Stabilizers, .. (2013)

-  Marshall - Difference and Discrimination in Psychotherapy and Counselling (2004)

-  Nobus & Quinn - Knowing Nothing, Staying Stupid; Elements for a Psychoanalytic Epistemology (2005)

-  Owen - Psychotherapy and Phenomenology; On Freud, Husserl and Heideggar (2006)

-  Razinsky - Freud, Psychoanalysis and Death (2013)

-  Shorter - A Historical Dictionary of Psychiatry (2005)

-  Stanovich - How to Think Straight about Psychology, 10e (2013)

-  Szasz - Antipsychiatry; Quackery Squared (2009)

-  Szasz - Psychiatry; the Science of Lies (Audio File)

-  Tauber - Requiem for the Ego; Freud and the Origins of Postmodernism (2013)

-  Williams et al (Eds.) - Independent Psychoanalysis Today (2012)

-  Wurtzel - Prozac Nation; Young and Depressed (1994)
